# Roadmap for LLM Studio

## Phase 1: Foundation Development (Q1-Q2 2024)
- Complete core platform architecture.
- Establish integrations with major blockchain protocols.
- Develop primary automation modules.

## Phase 2: Beta Launch (Q3 2024)
- Open beta release to select users.
- Collect and incorporate user feedback.
- Deploy initial dashboard and data analytics tools.

## Phase 3: Feature Expansion and Security Enhancements (Q4 2024)
- Introduce advanced workflow automation.
- Conduct comprehensive security audits.
- Expand community engagement and support tools.

## Phase 4: Full Launch and Ecosystem Integration (Q1 2025)
- Official stable version release.
- Onboard partners and third-party integrations.
- Publish detailed documentation and training resources.

## Key Milestones
- Core MVP ready.
- Beta feedback cycle completed.
- Security validations.
- Strategic partnership announcements.

## Short-Term Goals
- Deliver a robust beta experience.
- Build an engaged user community.

## Long-Term Goals
- Become the standard automation tool for web3 projects.
- Support cross-chain compatibility.
- Expand globally with multi-language support.

## Future Expansion
- AI-driven predictive analytics.
- Decentralized governance features.
- Enhanced developer SDKs.